This is a placeholder for Bank_Account_Form.pdf

In a real implementation, this would be a PDF form with fillable fields including:

- Applicant Full Name
- Date of Birth
- Residential Address
- Phone Number
- Email Address
- PAN Number
- Aadhaar Number
- Occupation
- Annual Income
- Nominee Name
- Nominee Relationship

The PDF would have interactive form fields that can be programmatically filled using the form filler component.
